&lt;li&gt;Develop process mapping documentation, user procedures, guidelines, and training documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, test and communicate to stakeholders any impact of Workday semi-annual release.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor Workday Community and maintain knowledge of Workday functionality and any updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
