&lt;li&gt;1 to 3 years of hands-on experience with Workday Core HCM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Core HCM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Workday design, structure, functions, and business processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and as part of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly professional with high ethical standards for handling confidential information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
